      "radius": {},
      "borderWidth": {},
      "description": "Ce composant Input fournit un champ de saisie de texte flexible avec trois tailles (sm, md, lg) et gère les états visuels (défaut, hover, focus, erreur, désactivé) en utilisant des tokens de design.\n\n```jsx\nconst Input = ({ \n  size = 'md', \n  error = false, \n  disabled = false, \n  placeholder = 'Entrez du texte',\n  ...props \n}) => (\n  <input\n    placeholder={placeholder}\n    disabled={disabled}\n    style={{\n      paddingLeft: `var(--component-input-size-${size}-paddingX)`,\n      paddingRight: `var(--component-input-size-${size}-paddingX)`,\n      paddingTop: `var(--component-input-size-${size}-paddingY)`,\n      paddingBottom: `var(--component-input-size-${size}-paddingY)`,\n      fontSize: `var(--component-input-size-${size}-fontSize)`,\n      minHeight: `var(--component-input-size-${size}-minHeight)`,\n      backgroundColor: disabled ? 'var(--component-input-bg-disabled)' : 'var(--component-input-bg-default)',\n      color: disabled ? 'var(--component-input-text-disabled)' : 'var(--component-input-text-default)',\n      borderWidth: 'var(--component-input-borderWidth)',\n      borderStyle: 'solid',\n      borderColor: error ? 'var(--component-input-border-error)' : disabled ? 'var(--component-input-border-disabled)' : 'var(--component-input-border-default)',\n      borderRadius: 'var(--component-input-radius)',\n      transition: 'border-color 0.2s ease',\n    }}\n    onMouseEnter={(e) => !disabled && !error && (e.target.style.borderColor = 'var(--component-input-border-hover)')}\n    onMouseLeave={(e) => !disabled && !error && (e.target.style.borderColor = 'var(--component-input-border-default)')}\n    onFocus={(e) => !disabled && (e.target.style.borderColor = 'var(--component-input-border-focus)')}\n    onBlur={(e) => !disabled && !error && (e.target.style.borderColor = 'var(--component-input-border-default)')}\n    {...props}\n  />\n);\n\nexport default Input;\n```"
    },
    "card": {
      "padding": {
        "sm": {},
